      "**Cold audience, conversion objective:** A hook rate above 30% is strong. 20-30% is average. Below 20% means your hook needs immediate work.",
      "**Retargeting, warm audience:** Benchmarks are higher because the audience already knows you — aim for above 40%. Below 30% on retargeting suggests your creative feels repetitive to this audience.",
      "**Static ads (images/carousels):** Hook rate translates to link click rate for static creative. Above 2.5% CTR on cold audiences is strong. Below 1.5% indicates a weak headline or visual.",
      "**UGC format:** UGC typically achieves 5-10% higher hook rates than polished studio creative on cold audiences, because it blends into the feed.",
      "## The 5 Hook Types Ranked by Average Hook Rate",
