      "## The 3 Scaling Methods That Work in 2026",
      "### Method 1: Horizontal Scaling (Best for Most Campaigns)",
      "Instead of increasing budget on one winning campaign, duplicate the campaign with different audiences. Each campaign runs independently with its own learning and its own audience segment.",
      "This preserves your original campaign's learning data while expanding reach. The new duplicate starts fresh learning, but your original keeps delivering at its proven efficiency.",
      "Works best when: you've identified multiple distinct audience segments (different lookalike percentages, different interests, different placements) and want to run each independently.",
      "### Method 2: Creative Scaling (Most Sustainable)",
